I don't run X draws. They've always seemed too Christmasland. I want to get consistent cards. If I have enough mana to draw a gross amount with an X draw I want to be using that X to win the game, not maybe win the game in a few turns off a big draw.
I do have a couple of ways to use the GY though.
Target though, yeah that's different Henry
I have a mix of draw X and others in all my decks
Just being able to sink everything into a full grip of cards is so good sometimes
And, of course, Mizzix loves them

I used to be on board with the X draw spells, but anymore I think they’re a trap if you’re just using them for huge greedy draws since it means leaving up so much mana on a regular basis which can easily lead to wasting it on average. I’d rather get a certain number of cards and still be able to do things with those cards.
I said I don't run any X draws, but I do have Sphinx's Rev in Isperia sphinxes, and it's only still in the deck because of flavor.
Most of the time I wish it was Treasure Cruise or Chart a Course
